snippet.title: Animal Crossing [57] GameCube Longplay pt.1
snippet.description:
Animal Crossing is a 2001 life simulation/role playing game. The player moves to a town filled with anthropomorphic animals and must work their way through debt by making money through the tanuki, Tom Nook and helping neighbors with miscellaneous tasks. Sounds like real life, right?

This longplay was requested by: Jeannette Silvia
